<i>noun</i>: 시냇물 [시ː낸물], 시내 [시ː내], 개천 [개천], 개울 [개울] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>시냇물 [시ː낸물]</dt><br>
<dd>stream; brook</dd><br>
<dd>골짜기나 들판에 흐르는 작은 물줄기의 물.</dd><br>
<dd>The water of a small stream that flows in a valley or plain.</dd><br>
<dt>시내 [시ː내]</dt><br>
<dd>stream; brook</dd><br>
<dd>골짜기나 들판에 흐르는 작은 물줄기.</dd><br>
<dd>A small stream that flows in a valley or plain.</dd><br>
<dt>개천 [개천]</dt><br>
<dd>brook; creek</dd><br>
<dd>시내보다 크고 강보다 작은 물줄기.</dd><br>
<dd>A water stream that is bigger than a streamlet and smaller than a river.</dd><br>
<dt>개울 [개울]</dt><br>
<dd>brook; small stream; creek</dd><br>
<dd>골짜기나 들에 흐르는 작은 물줄기.</dd><br>
<dd>A small stream of water running through a valley or a meadow.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>